uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network

Class NFeature<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.NEntity
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.NFeature<V>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NDataFeature, NLink

    public abstract class NFeature<V>
extends NEntity
    Represents a feature attached to a node in the network-based instance representation. Features can be of either link or data-valued type.
